Beyond the Summit Sessions
The civic community is the real beneficiary of any health programme. So, IAST 2023 has a few specially designed programs for the public at large:

Speciality medical clinics in all five disciplines of AYUSH
AYUSH speciality awareness stalls, AYUSH medicinal plant expo, AYUSH healthy food court
AYUSH awareness classes and public lectures
Release of books & journals
Yoga demonstrations from 6:30 am to 7:30 am on all three days of the summit at the Summit site, By yoga Acharyas
